Package: rhythm.metrics
Title: Analyse and Visualise Rhythm Metrics
Version: 1.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Cong",
           family = "Zhang",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "cong.zhang@newcastle.ac.uk",
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-2561-2113"))
Description: This package is designed for calculating and visualising 
    speech rhythm metrics. It provides functions for the calculation of 
    Delta C, Delta V, VarcoC, VarcoV, %V, rPVI_C, and nPVI_V.
